\">MOD_FOO=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;[PROJECT_NAME]&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">MOD_FOO_XML_DESCRIPTION=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Foo Module&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">MOD_FOO_FIELD_URL_LABEL=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;URL&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">COM_MODULES_FOOPARAMS_FIELDSET_LABEL=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;Foo Parameter&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span></code></pre>\n<!-- prettier-ignore -->\n<h5 id=\"modulesmod_foo-mod_foophp\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#modulesmod_foo-mod_foophp\" aria-label=\"modulesmod_foo mod_foophp permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>modules/mod_foo/ mod_foo.php</h5>\n<p>In the module's initial file