s=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t&lt;/config&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> &lt;/extension&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span></code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Use <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;fieldset name=\"basic\"></code> to display the parameters in the first tab that opens immediately.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>In addition to the parameters that a developer inserts into his module, there are standard parameters that Joomla handles itself. For example <code class=\"language-text\">/administrator/components/com_modules/forms/advanced.xml</code>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/191e2/j4x38x1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Joomla Module Parameters\"\n        title=\"Joomla Module Parameters\"\n        src=\"/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/5a190/j4x38x1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/772e8/j4x38x1.png 200w,\n/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/e17e5/j4x38x1.png 400w,\n/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/5a190/j4x38x1.png 800w,\n/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/c1b63/j4x38x1.png 1200w,\n/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/29007/j4x38x1.png 1600w,\n/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/191e2/j4x38x1.png 1836w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<!-- prettier-ignore -->\n<h5 id=\"modulesmod_footmpldefaultphp\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#modulesmod_footmpldefaultphp\" aria-label=\"modulesmod_footmpldefaultphp permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>modules/mod_foo/tmpl/default.php</h5>\n<p>In the module's own template file, we can now access the value of the parameter. In the following example, we output the value as text. Usually a parameter is used in a more complex way, for example within control structures such as if-statements or loops.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>An example of the more complex use of a parameter is a digital map where parameters are used to enable controls such as <code class=\"language-text\">locate me</code> or a choice of map type.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/blob/b8c783812c9acf66a6c0c0a534d5d43b987510c5/src/modules/mod_foo/tmpl/default.php\">modules/mod_foo/tmpl/default.php</a></p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container grvsc-has-line-highlighting default-dark\" data-language=\"php\" data-index=\"3\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> \\</span><span class=\"mtk11\">defined</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;_JEXEC&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">) or </span><span class=\"mtk15\">die</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-del\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-del\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"-\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">echo</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;[PROJECT_NAME]&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> . </span><span class=\"mtk12\">$test</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">echo</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;[PROJECT_NAME]&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> . </span><span class=\"mtk12\">$test</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> . </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;&lt;br /&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> . </span><span class=\"mtk12\">$url</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"test-your-joomla-module\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#test-your-joomla-module\" aria-label=\"test your joomla module permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"